{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/make/word-clock.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>I followed instructions from Make magazine (Volume 67) and I made a word clock.</p>\n<p>I also started a <a href=\"https://repl.it/@stakanmartini/WordClock#main.cpp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">code project</a> for discovering ways to place words on a grid. With all possible optimization like shaping words in a form of crossword.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.4954128440366972;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/63f48a69a8534a4b4d54b6b898b3dd31/3acf0/word-clock-1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.87116564417178%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Acryl is ready\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/63f48a69a8534a4b4d54b6b898b3dd31/6aca1/word-clock-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/63f48a69a8534a4b4d54b6b898b3dd31/d2f63/word-clock-1.jpg 163w,\n/static/63f48a69a8534a4b4d54b6b898b3dd31/c989d/word-clock-1.jpg 325w,\n/static/63f48a69a8534a4b4d54b6b898b3dd31/6aca1/word-clock-1.jpg 650w,\n/static/63f48a69a8534a4b4d54b6b898b3dd31/7c09c/word-clock-1.jpg 975w,\n/static/63f48a69a8534a4b4d54b6b898b3dd31/01ab0/word-clock-1.jpg 1300w,\n/static/63f48a69a8534a4b4d54b6b898b3dd31/3acf0/word-clock-1.jpg 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"why\" style=\"position:relative;\">Why<a href=\"#why\" aria-label=\"why permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>It will stay on the table and will show time when I need to head out of the office.</p>\n<h2 id=\"process\" style=\"position:relative;\">Process<a href=\"#process\" aria-label=\"process permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>Ordered laser cut</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.4954128440366972;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/95422de4fd9305bdca71d70b7c806fde/3acf0/word-clock-2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.87116564417178%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Peel it\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/95422de4fd9305bdca71d70b7c806fde/6aca1/word-clock-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/95422de4fd9305bdca71d70b7c806fde/d2f63/word-clock-2.jpg 163w,\n/static/95422de4fd9305bdca71d70b7c806fde/c989d/word-clock-2.jpg 325w,\n/static/95422de4fd9305bdca71d70b7c806fde/6aca1/word-clock-2.jpg 650w,\n/static/95422de4fd9305bdca71d70b7c806fde/7c09c/word-clock-2.jpg 975w,\n/static/95422de4fd9305bdca71d70b7c806fde/01ab0/word-clock-2.jpg 1300w,\n/static/95422de4fd9305bdca71d70b7c806fde/3acf0/word-clock-2.jpg 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Bought screws and adafruit boards. In the original instructions it used <a href=\"https://www.adafruit.com/product/2000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Trinket Pro 5V</a> (ATmega328), but I followed the deprecation warning and chose <a href=\"https://www.adafruit.com/product/3677\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Adafruit ItsyBitsy 32u4 - 5V 16MHz</a> (Atmega32u4). Imprtant difference between them: the latter is missing mount holes which is the only way to attach the board to the acrylic case inside. I put it inside the case loosely, thus the USB connector become impossible to connect back once you unplug it, so one USB cable took roots in this build for a long time.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.4954128440366972;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6f32df6aacae6dbccbedb3cc3e40052b/3acf0/word-clock-3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.87116564417178%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"The case parts\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/6f32df6aacae6dbccbedb3cc3e40052b/6aca1/word-clock-3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6f32df6aacae6dbccbedb3cc3e40052b/d2f63/word-clock-3.jpg 163w,\n/static/6f32df6aacae6dbccbedb3cc3e40052b/c989d/word-clock-3.jpg 325w,\n/static/6f32df6aacae6dbccbedb3cc3e40052b/6aca1/word-clock-3.jpg 650w,\n/static/6f32df6aacae6dbccbedb3cc3e40052b/7c09c/word-clock-3.jpg 975w,\n/static/6f32df6aacae6dbccbedb3cc3e40052b/01ab0/word-clock-3.jpg 1300w,\n/static/6f32df6aacae6dbccbedb3cc3e40052b/3acf0/word-clock-3.jpg 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>How do you call screen that does not display time with digits, but tells it with words?</p>\n<h2 id=\"result\" style=\"position:relative;\">Result<a href=\"#result\" aria-label=\"result permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.2255639097744362;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e1fce3d2196bfe08d54295a2fa4caf3d/9c311/word-clock-4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81.59509202453987%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"The case is assembled\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/e1fce3d2196bfe08d54295a2fa4caf3d/6aca1/word-clock-4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e1fce3d2196bfe08d54295a2fa4caf3d/d2f63/word-clock-4.jpg 163w,\n/static/e1fce3d2196bfe08d54295a2fa4caf3d/c989d/word-clock-4.jpg 325w,\n/static/e1fce3d2196bfe08d54295a2fa4caf3d/6aca1/word-clock-4.jpg 650w,\n/static/e1fce3d2196bfe08d54295a2fa4caf3d/9c311/word-clock-4.jpg 838w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>The clock is working.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; flex:1.2348484848484849;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fb844f6ff8e0f80e27c7719057e6790e/a4b7e/word-clock-5.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: bl